citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:20pm on 19-
JAN-2023.
The inspector arrived at the facility at 12:20pm and called the licensee and left a message. The inspector also knocked
on the door of the house and honked the horn of the vehicle. Directly across the road is a dog kennel and the inspector
drove to the kennel area and honked the horn. After waiting 30 minutes the inspector left the facility.
End Section

narrative:
2.126(b) 
   
Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries. 
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:20pm on 19-
JAN-2023. 
 
The inspector arrived at the facility at 12:20pm and called the licensee and left a message.  The inspector also knocked 
on the door of the house and honked the horn of the vehicle.  Directly across the road is a dog kennel and the inspector 
drove to the kennel area and honked the horn.  After waiting 30 minutes the inspector left the facility. 
 
 
 
End Section
